              </p>
              <p>
                Handoff uses reasonable efforts to ensure that the Services are available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week. However, there will be occasions when the Services will be interrupted for maintenance, upgrades and repairs, or as a result of failure of telecommunications links and equipment that are beyond the control of Handoff. Every reasonable step will be taken by Handoff to minimize such disruption where it is within the reasonable control of Handoff. You agree that Handoff shall not be liable to you for any modification, suspension or discontinuance of the Services.
              </p>
              <p>
                You shall be responsible for obtaining and maintaining any equipment or ancillary services needed to connect to, access the Services or otherwise use the Services, including, without limitation, modems, hardware, software, and long distance or local telephone service. You shall be responsible for ensuring that such equipment or ancillary services are compatible with the Services.
              </p>

              <hr />

              <!-- 3. Infringing Content; DMCA -->
              <h2 id="infringing-content">Infringing Content; DMCA</h2>
