                If you believe that your copyright-protected work has been used on the Services in a way that constitutes copyright infringement, you may submit a notification pursuant to the Digital Millennium Copyright Act ("DMCA") to our designated agent. Notifications should be sent to <a href="mailto:support@handoff.ai">support@handoff.ai</a>. To be effective, your DMCA notification must include the following:
