              </p>
              <p>
                You must not use the Services to transmit illegal, harmful, offensive, or infringing content. Respect the rights of others and do not engage in behavior that disrupts the service experience for other users.
              </p>
              <p>
                When using the voice-to-text feature, you agree not to submit any sensitive personal information or confidential data through voice input, including but not limited to social security numbers, credit card numbers, or other financial information. You are responsible for reviewing and editing the transcribed text before submitting it as part of your project description or estimate.
              </p>

              <hr />

              <!-- 6. Handoff and Electronic Signature -->
              <h2 id="electronic-signature">Handoff and Electronic Signature</h2>
              <p>
                By using the Site and the Services, particularly the Handoff service, you expressly consent to the use of electronic signatures for the purpose of generating estimates for customers and electronically signing these estimates and other related documents.
              </p>
              <p>You acknowledge and agree that:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Your electronic signature on documents is legally binding and has the same force and effect as a handwritten signature under the Electronic Signatures in Global and National Commerce Act (E-Sign Act), the Uniform Electronic Transactions Act (UETA), and other applicable state and federal laws.</li>
                <li>You have the right to withdraw your consent to use electronic signatures at any time by contacting us at <a href="mailto:support@handoff.ai">support@handoff.ai</a>. However, if you withdraw your consent, you may not be able to use certain features of the Handoff service.</li>
